💡 Prompt Manager: Main Dashboard Design Specification
1. 디자인 철학 및 테마
테마: Modern Dark Mode (VS Code 및 Linear 스타일 참고)
주요 색상:
Background: #1E1E1E (메인 배경)
Sidebar: #252526 (패널 배경)
Accent: #007ACC (포인트 블루 - 실행 버튼 및 활성 탭)
Text: Primary #D4D4D4, Secondary #858585
Highlight: #CE9178 (프롬프트 내 {{variable}} 태그 강조색)
폰트:
UI: Segoe UI 또는 Inter (10pt)
Editor: Consolas 또는 Fira Code (12pt, 고정폭 폰트)
2. 레이아웃 구조 (3-Column Architecture)
애플리케이션은 QSplitter를 사용하여 사용자가 각 패널의 너비를 자유롭게 조절할 수 있는 구조입니다.

[좌측 패널] Task Navigator (Width: 250px)
상단: Search Bar (태스크 검색) 및 'New Task' 버튼 (QPushButton with icon).
중앙: 태스크 리스트 (QListWidget 또는 QTreeView).
각 항목은 태스크 이름과 최종 수정 시간을 표시.
선택된 태스크는 강조 표시(background-color: #37373D).
하단: 애플리케이션 설정 및 사용자 프로필 버튼.
[중앙 패널] Prompt Editor (Main Area)
가장 핵심적인 작업 영역으로, 상단 탭(QTabBar)을 통해 **'Editor'**와 'Variables' 모드를 전환합니다.

System Prompt Section (Top):
레이블: SYSTEM PROMPT (작고 연한 폰트)
입력창: QPlainTextEdit (높이 고정, 약 150px). LLM의 페르소나와 규칙을 정의.
User Prompt Section (Middle):
레이블: USER PROMPT
입력창: QPlainTextEdit (가변 높이). 실제 명령어를 작성하며 {{variable}} 입력 시 하이라이팅 적용.
Variable Quick-Panel (Right Sidebar - Toggleable):
QDockWidget 형태로 구현되어 접었다 폈다 할 수 있음.
현재 프롬프트에서 감지된 변수들을 리스트업하고 즉시 값을 입력할 수 있는 필드 제공.
[우측 패널] Result Viewer & Metrics (Width: 350px)
상단 제어바:
Model Selector (QComboBox): OpenAI, Ollama, vLLM 선택.
RUN 버튼: 크고 직관적인 파란색 버튼. 실행 중에는 로딩 애니메이션 표시.
결과창: QTextBrowser (Markdown 렌더링 지원). LLM의 응답이 실시간 스트리밍 형태로 출력됨.
하단 메트릭 바 (Status Bar):
Latency: 1.2s, Input Tokens: 45, Output Tokens: 120, Cost: $0.002 등 핵심 정보 표시.
3. 핵심 사용자 경험 (UX) 디테일
A. 변수 감지 및 동기화
사용자가 프롬프트 에디터에 {{를 입력하면 자동 완성(IntelliSense) 팝업이 뜨며 기존 변수를 제안합니다.
에디터에서 새로운 변수를 생성하면 우측의 Quick-Panel에 즉시 입력 필드가 생성됩니다.
B. 버전 타임라인
중앙 상단에 작은 브레드크럼(Breadcrumb) 또는 버전 번호(v1.2.4)를 표시합니다.
클릭 시 드롭다운으로 이전 버전 목록이 타임라인 형태로 나타나며, 선택 시 즉시 에디터 내용이 교체됩니다.
C. 접기/펴기 기능 (Collapsible UI)
좌측/우측 패널 경계선에 작은 화살표 버튼을 배치하여 클릭 한 번으로 패널을 숨길 수 있습니다. 프롬프트 작성에만 집중하고 싶을 때 유용합니다.
4. PySide6 구현 팁
Syntax Highlighting: QSyntaxHighlighter 클래스를 상속받아 {{...}} 패턴에 대한 정규식 하이라이팅을 구현하세요.
Markdown Rendering: QTextBrowser의 setMarkdown() 기능을 사용하면 LLM의 응답을 예쁘게 보여줄 수 있습니다.
Asynchronous API: API 호출 시 GUI가 멈추지 않도록 QThread나 QRunnable을 사용하여 비동기로 통신하고, 결과를 Signal로 받아 UI를 업데이트하세요.
이 상세 명세가 프로젝트 개발에 도움이 되길 바랍니다! 추가로 특정 부분의 코드 구조나 QSS 스타일 예시가 필요하시면 말씀해 주세요.

---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="dark" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Prompt Manager Dashboard</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons+Round" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#2b8cee",
                        "background-light": "#f6f7f8",
                        "background-dark": "#101922",
                        "panel-dark": "#15202b",
                        "border-dark": "#1e2d3b",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Space Grotesk", "sans-serif"],
                        "mono": ["JetBrains Mono", "monospace"],
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style>
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #101922; 
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #2b3b4f; 
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #3b4e66; 
        }
        .syntax-variable {
            color: #2b8cee;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-display h-screen flex overflow-hidden selection:bg-primary/30">
<aside class="w-64 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark bg-white dark:bg-panel-dark">
<div class="h-14 flex items-center px-4 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-primary">terminal</span>
<span class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">PromptMngr</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="p-4">
<div class="relative group">
<span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3 text-slate-400 group-focus-within:text-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">search</span>
</span>
<input class="w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-background-dark text-sm rounded-lg pl-9 pr-3 py-2 border-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary placeholder-slate-500 dark:placeholder-slate-600 transition-all" placeholder="Search tasks..." type="text"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-2 space-y-1">
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-3 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary group transition-all">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
<span class="font-medium text-sm truncate">Customer Support Bot</span>
<span class="material-icons-round text-[16px] opacity-100">edit</span>
</div>
<div class="text-xs opacity-70 truncate">v1.4 • Last edited 2m ago</div>
</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark border border-transparent text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-200 transition-all group">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
<span class="font-medium text-sm truncate">Python Code Refactor</span>
<span class="material-icons-round text-[16px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">edit</span>
</div>
<div class="text-xs opacity-50 truncate">v2.1 • 5h ago</div>
</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark border border-transparent text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-200 transition-all group">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
<span class="font-medium text-sm truncate">Blog Post Generator</span>
<span class="material-icons-round text-[16px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">edit</span>
</div>
<div class="text-xs opacity-50 truncate">v1.0 • Yesterday</div>
</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark border border-transparent text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-200 transition-all group">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
<span class="font-medium text-sm truncate">SQL Query Helper</span>
<span class="material-icons-round text-[16px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">edit</span>
</div>
<div class="text-xs opacity-50 truncate">v3.2 • 2 days ago</div>
</button>
</div>
<div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark">
<button class="flex items-center justify-center w-full gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-background-dark hover:text-primary hover:border-primary transition-all text-sm font-medium">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">add</span>
<span>New Task</span>
</button>
</div>
</aside>
<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-[400px] border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
<header class="h-14 flex items-center justify-between px-6 bg-white dark:bg-panel-dark border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark flex-shrink-0">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<h1 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-white">Customer Support Bot</h1>
<span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-primary/20 text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Draft</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400">
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark rounded-lg hover:text-primary transition-colors tooltip" title="Save">
<span class="material-icons-round text-xl">save</span>
</button>
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark rounded-lg hover:text-primary transition-colors" title="History">
<span class="material-icons-round text-xl">history</span>
</button>
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark rounded-lg hover:text-primary transition-colors" title="Settings">
<span class="material-icons-round text-xl">settings</span>
</button>
</div>
</header>
<div class="flex flex-col flex-1 overflow-hidden relative">
<div class="flex items-center px-4 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0d131a]">
<button class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary border-b-2 border-primary flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">edit_note</span> Editor
                </button>
<button class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">data_object</span> Variables 
                    <span class="bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-xs px-1.5 rounded-full">2</span>
</button>
<button class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">tune</span> Config
                </button>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden bg-[#1e2329] dark:bg-[#0d131a]">
<div class="flex flex-col border-b border-slate-700/50 h-[30%] min-h-[150px]">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100/5 dark:bg-white/5 border-b border-slate-700/50">
<label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm text-slate-500">settings_system_daydream</span> System Prompt
                        </label>
<span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">Instructions for the AI persona</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex relative">
<div class="flex flex-col text-slate-600 select-none pr-3 pl-4 text-right min-w-[40px] font-mono text-xs pt-3 bg-[#1e2329] dark:bg-[#0d131a] border-r border-slate-700/30">
<span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span>
</div>
<textarea class="flex-1 bg-[#1e2329] dark:bg-[#0d131a] text-slate-300 p-3 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed resize-none focus:outline-none border-none custom-scrollbar" spellcheck="false">You are an expert helpful assistant for TechCorp. Your tone should be professional, empathetic, and concise. Never hallucinate features we don't have.</textarea>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col min-h-[200px]">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100/5 dark:bg-white/5 border-b border-slate-700/50">
<label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm text-slate-500">person</span> User Prompt
                        </label>
<span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">The task to execute</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex relative overflow-auto custom-scrollbar">
<div class="flex flex-col text-slate-600 select-none pr-3 pl-4 text-right min-w-[40px] font-mono text-xs pt-3 bg-[#1e2329] dark:bg-[#0d131a] border-r border-slate-700/30 h-full">
<span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span><span>6</span><span>7</span><span>8</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 outline-none text-slate-300 selection:bg-primary/40 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words p-3 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed bg-[#1e2329] dark:bg-[#0d131a]" contenteditable="true" spellcheck="false">Please analyze the following customer complaint: 
<span class="syntax-variable">{{complaint_text}}</span>
Identify the core issue and the customer's sentiment. Then, suggest a polite, empathetic response based on our policy document: 
<span class="syntax-variable">{{policy_doc}}</span>
Ensure the tone is professional yet warm. Do not admit fault directly but offer solutions.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-panel-dark border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark p-4 shadow-[0_-4px_6px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] z-20 flex-shrink-0">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="relative w-64">
<select class="w-full appearance-none bg-slate-100 dark:bg-background-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 pr-8 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary cursor-pointer font-medium">
<option>OpenAI: GPT-4o</option>
<option>OpenAI: GPT-3.5-Turbo</option>
<option>Anthropic: Claude 3.5</option>
<option>Local: Llama 3 (Ollama)</option>
</select>
<span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none text-slate-500">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">expand_more</span>
</span>
</div>
<div class="h-8 w-[1px] bg-slate-200 dark:bg-border-dark mx-2"></div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-400">
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider mb-0.5">Temp</span>
<span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-mono">0.7</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider mb-0.5">Max Tokens</span>
<span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 font-mono">2k</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1"></div>
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-all active:scale-95">
<span class="material-icons-round text-lg">play_arrow</span>
                        Run
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
<aside class="w-[300px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0f161e] hidden md:flex">
<header class="h-14 flex items-center justify-between px-5 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark flex-shrink-0">
<h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
<span class="material-icons-round text-slate-400 text-lg">data_object</span>
                 Test Variables
             </h2>
<span class="text-xs bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">2</span>
</header>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 space-y-4">
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-2">Define values for variables found in your prompt templates.</p>
<div class="space-y-1.5 group">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
<label class="text-xs font-mono text-primary flex items-center gap-1">
<span class="bg-primary/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-primary/20">{{complaint_text}}</span>
</label>
<button class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-opacity">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">edit</span>
</button>
</div>
<textarea class="w-full bg-white dark:bg-background-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark rounded-lg text-sm px-3 py-2 h-32 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary resize-none placeholder-slate-400 shadow-sm" placeholder="Enter value...">My internet has been down for 3 days and nobody is answering my tickets! I want a refund immediately.</textarea>
</div>
<div class="space-y-1.5 group">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
<label class="text-xs font-mono text-primary flex items-center gap-1">
<span class="bg-primary/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-primary/20">{{policy_doc}}</span>
</label>
<button class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-opacity">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">edit</span>
</button>
</div>
<textarea class="w-full bg-white dark:bg-background-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark rounded-lg text-sm px-3 py-2 h-32 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary resize-none placeholder-slate-400 shadow-sm" placeholder="Enter value...">Standard Policy: Issues unresolved for &gt;48h qualify for 10% credit. Refunds only for full outage &gt; 7 days.</textarea>
</div>
<button class="w-full py-2 border border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-xs text-slate-500 hover:text-primary hover:border-primary hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-sm">add</span> Add Test Case
            </button>
</div>
</aside>
<aside class="flex-1 min-w-[350px] max-w-[500px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col bg-white dark:bg-panel-dark border-l border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark">
<header class="h-14 flex items-center justify-between px-5 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark flex-shrink-0">
<h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-icons-round text-primary text-lg">auto_awesome</span>
                Result
            </h2>
<div class="flex gap-1">
<button class="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-primary hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark rounded transition-colors" title="Copy">
<span class="material-icons-round text-lg">content_copy</span>
</button>
<button class="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-primary hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-background-dark rounded transition-colors" title="Regenerate">
<span class="material-icons-round text-lg">refresh</span>
</button>
</div>
</header>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-panel-dark custom-scrollbar">
<div class="prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert prose-p:text-slate-600 dark:prose-p:text-slate-300 max-w-none">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
<span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 font-medium border border-green-500/20">Success</span>
<span>Generated in 1.2s</span>
</div>
<p class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4">Suggested Response Draft:</p>
<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-background-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-border-dark shadow-sm">
<p class="mb-3">Dear Customer,</p>
<p class="mb-3">I completely understand how frustrating it is to be without internet service for three days, especially when you feel your tickets haven't been addressed promptly. I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience this outage has caused you.</p>
<p class="mb-3">Regarding your request for a refund: While our policy typically issues refunds for full outages lasting longer than 7 days, I can see that your issue has been unresolved for over 48 hours. Therefore, I have applied a <strong>10% credit</strong> to your account immediately as a gesture of goodwill.</p>
<p>I have escalated your ticket to our priority queue. A technician should be in touch within the next 4 hours.</p>
<p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 italic">TechCorp Support Team</p>
</div>
