<ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
<li><strong>Issue:</strong> 3-day internet outage, unresponsive support.</li>
<li><strong>Sentiment:</strong> Angry, frustrated.</li>
<li><strong>Action:</strong> Applied 10% credit per &gt;48h policy rule.</li>
</ul>
</div>
